  "texts": [
    "Another concern is related to the performance metrics.",
    "Indeed, canonical metrics like precision, recall, and F1-score may not suffice to assess these tools.",
    "For instance, for the screening phase, it is critical to minimise the costs of screening while preserving a high recall.",
    "For this reason, it was suggested to adopt the F2 score (Sumbul et al. 2021) instead of the F1 score.",
    "The F2 score is computed as the weighted harmonic mean of precision and recall."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "For this reason, it was suggested to adopt the F2 score (Sumbul et al. 2021) instead of the F1 score."
  ]
